                        <interp inst="t18711023-736-offence-2" type="offenceSubcategory" value="assault"></interp>There was another indictment against the Prisoner for an assault on the same person,</rs> 
                     <rs id="t18711023-736-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18711023-736-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
